(385, 1, '2015-07-01 08:25:21', '2015-07-01 08:25:21', 'There are plenty of things to see and do north of <strong>Perth</strong>; an area rich in history, nature, culture and beauty. Since the opening of the new Indian Ocean Drive between Lancelin and Cervantes, a trip to the famous Pinnacles and beyond can now include much more. Within a three hour drive of <strong>Perth</strong> there is a selection of interesting and unique attractions to enjoy.\r\n\r\nBreak your trip up, take your time and enjoy pristine natural bush, wildlife, spectacular coast, wide open roads, fresh air and abundant wildflowers. At Yanchep National Park you''ll discover beautiful national park lands, kangaroos, koalas, ancient caves, walk trails, Aboriginal culture and peaceful picnic spots. Ride through natural bushland on horseback, or enjoy devonshire teas while learning about science and the universe at the Gravity Discovery Centre, just ten minutes north of Yanchep.\r\n\r\nUsing the fishing town of Cervantes as a base, visit the famous <strong>Pinnacles</strong> at the nearby Nambung National Park which is approximately a two hour drive north of <strong>Perth</strong>. Attracting over 190,000 visitors a year, these amazing natural limestone structures were formed approximately 25,000 years ago. Near Cervantes you can also discover the Stromatolites at Lake Thetis, which are the some of the world''s oldest fossils, providing the most ancient records of life on earth. For more information visit the Pinnacles Visitor Centre on Cadiz Street in Cervantes.\r\n\r\nHeading further north take a drive along the stunning Turquoise Coast to the quaint sea side town of <strong>Jurien Bay</strong>, which is home to the Jurien Bay Marine Park, resident sea lions and during migration season from June to December, the majestic humpback whales. For the adventure seeker, <strong>Jurien Bay</strong> is also home to the famous Skydive Jurien Bay! See below for a selection of activities and attractions throughout the North of <strong>Perth</strong> area or for more information, visit: <a href="http://www.australiascoralcoast.com/" target="_blank">australiascoralcoast.com.au.</a>', 'North of Perth', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'north-of-perth', '', '', '2015-07-01 08:25:21', '2015-07-01 08:25:21', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?page_id=385', 0, 'page', '', 0),
