(391, 1, '2015-07-01 08:45:46', '2015-07-01 08:45:46', 'Perth offers a great selection of attractions and activities, with plenty of things to do and experience. Whether you are an adventure seeker or have a young family, there is something to suit all tastes and budgets. Beautiful open parks, the best beaches and weather in the world,  fabulous diving, islands,  wildlife, national parks, shopping, nightlife, theatre and culture; there’s much to choose from.\r\n\r\nGo for a dive, go fishing, horseriding, whale watching, swim with dolphins, or simply relax with a picnic in the one of the many picturesque parks. Go bush walking up in the Perth Hills, take a day tour up to the famous Pinnacles, pat some friendly kangaroos, sample world class wine in the Swan Valley, watch some gold pouring or take a camel ride through the natural Australian bush. Enjoy the majestic views overlooking the Perth Kings Park, or learn about the city with a open top, double decker bus tour.\r\n\r\nSpend a few days in historic Fremantle; full of colour with busy restaurants, cafes and bars trading all hours of the day and night. Browse through heritage markets, bookstores and museums. Enjoy fresh fish and chips at the Fishing Boat Harbour or pizza and pasta along the Cappuccino Strip, or visit one of the sylish microbreweries who offer an incredible range of amber ales.\r\n\r\nTake a wine tour through the Swan Valley, or cruise up the Swan River while tasting our world class wines. Indulge in local produce such as olives, cheese, coffee and free chocolate tastings at the Margaret River Chocolate Factory in the Swan Valley. Browse the antique and homeware stores in Guildford, or horseride, cycle, play golf or walk the historic walk trails.\r\n\r\nSee below for a selection of interesting activities or visit the Visitor Centre in William Street, and ask the helpful staff', 'See and Do', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'see-and-do', '', '', '2015-07-01 08:45:46', '2015-07-01 08:45:46', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?page_id=391', 0, 'page', '', 0),
