(397, 1, '2015-07-01 08:47:54', '2015-07-01 08:47:54', 'Perth offers a wide range of holiday accommodation to suit all budgets and all locations. You will find something to satisfy even the fussiest travellers from luxury hotels, self catered or contained apartments, B&amp;B’s, farm stays to private beach houses, budget hotels and for those on a tighter budget, hostels, backpackers, even camping grounds for the more adventurous.\r\n\r\nDepending on the time of the year, you will find prices competitive, but always best to shop around. It’s also good to check what major events are on in the city as this can impact on accommodation costs, especially in inner city hotels. Of course, booking well in advance also has its advantages and great bargains can be had from websites like wotif and LateRooms.\r\n\r\nHotels are graded using the star system, five star for luxury, down to two star which is more basic, but can still be very comfortable. Self contained apartments will suit families or groups traveling together and are especially good for longer stays, but make sure you book well in advance.\r\n\r\nWe have included a selection of local accommodation below, but for a more comprehensive list, to compare prices or to search for something more specific, please visit <a href="http://www.trivago.com.au/" target="_blank">www.trivago.com.au. </a>', 'Perth Accomodation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'perth-accomodation', '', '', '2015-07-01 08:48:05', '2015-07-01 08:48:05', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?page_id=397', 0, 'page', '', 0),
