(444, 1, '2015-07-08 04:24:58', '2015-07-08 04:24:58', 'A hidden gem tucked in a laneway off Murray Street. Winner of the 2014 WA Best Cocktail Bar award, this world class Cocktail, Tapas & Free Live Jazz lounge is a must for all Perth visitors. The lounge is elegant and refined, like pieces of New Orleans and old Paris transported to the heart of Perth. Walk-ins and bookings welcome. Tues - Sun 4pm til late. ', 'The Laneway Longue', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-laneway-longue', '', '', '2015-07-22 06:40:45', '2015-07-22 06:40:45', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=444', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
