(450, 1, '2015-07-08 04:38:53', '2015-07-08 04:38:53', 'The Trustee Bar and Bistro can be found in the Majestic WA Trustee Building in the heart of the CBD. This multi award-winning venue has quickly cemented itself as one of Perth’s favorite dining options. The Trustee offers two different levels with several spaces in which to enjoy their seasonal, bistro style menu. The downstairs bistro bustles with booth style seating, exposed wood and low ceilings which exude beautiful warmth that is perfect for a long leisurely lunch or a special dinner & upstairs their newly renovated rum bar is perfect for a well made cocktail, a glass of wine or an ice cold beer.', 'The Trustee Bar & Bistro', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-trustee-bar-bistro', '', '', '2015-07-08 04:38:53', '2015-07-08 04:38:53', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=450', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
