(454, 1, '2015-07-08 04:47:11', '2015-07-08 04:47:11', 'Visit Perth’s first maternity hospital which today displays many facets of medical history including nursing, dentistry, early medicine and the famous Royal Flying Doctor Service. Open Wednesday 10.30am - 4pm and the second and fourth Sunday of every month from 2pm - 4pm. Admission is $4 for adults and $1 for children.', 'WA Medical Museum', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wa-medical-museum', '', '', '2015-07-08 04:47:11', '2015-07-08 04:47:11', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=454', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
