(456, 1, '2015-07-08 04:51:41', '2015-07-08 04:51:41', 'Leave your world behind with Skydive the Beach and Beyond, with an unforgettable tandem skydive from the closest skydiving centre to the Perth CBD. Experience the thrill of freefall from up to 14,000ft before you float under canopy, taking in spectacular panorama views of the Perth CBD, the Swan River, WA beaches and beyond. Plus, with locations at Rockingham beach and York (where you can learn to skydive solo), you can choose the perfect backdrop. Capture your exhilarating experience with high-res photos and an edited video to relive the action. Gift vouchers also available.', 'Skydive the Beach & Beyond', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'skydive-the-beach-beyond', '', '', '2015-07-08 04:51:41', '2015-07-08 04:51:41', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=456', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
