(461, 1, '2015-07-08 04:56:11', '2015-07-08 04:56:11', 'Funcats is one of Perth''s iconic must do activities and one of the few places in the world where you can sail directly in front of a major city. With no experience necessary, there is no better way to enjoy our picturesque city than a relaxing sail on the beautiful Swan River. The fleet includes 40 catamarans, stand up paddleboards and kayaks. Catch the ferry across to South Perth and walk along the foreshore for eight minutes. No bookings required and a free lesson is included for those who haven''t sailed before.', 'Funcats Catamaran Hire', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'funcats-catamaran-hire', '', '', '2015-07-08 04:56:41', '2015-07-08 04:56:41', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=461', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
