(463, 1, '2015-07-08 04:59:08', '2015-07-08 04:59:08', 'Ever wanted to get up-close to a wallaby? Perth Zoo’s new ‘Bush Buddies’ experience lets you get Eye to Eye with this vulnerable species as well as a host of other critters including an adorable Quokka and Short-beaked Echidna. If scaly animals are more your thing, a Perth Zoo ‘Scaly Mates’ experience will be up your alley. Meet the Radiated Tortoise which literally fit in the palm of your hand, lizards and the vibrant, but sadly endangered Woma Pythons. Open every day of the year from 9am-5pm.', 'Perth Zoo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'perth-zoo', '', '', '2015-07-15 06:29:05', '2015-07-15 06:29:05', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=463', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
