(471, 1, '2015-07-08 05:31:14', '2015-07-08 05:31:14', 'enex100 is Perth’s centre of urban cool featuring three levels of fashion, food and lifestyle. enex100 is the centre of Australian fashion with an exclusive and coveted mix of designer labels for him and her including Calibre, Calvin Klein Jeans, Gorman, Jack London, Lisa Ho, lululemon athletica, Marcs and Mimco. Enjoy award winning food offers seven days a week at selected licensed retailers in the Food Podium with free live entertainment on Sundays and Friday nights.', 'enex100', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'enex100', '', '', '2015-07-08 05:31:14', '2015-07-08 05:31:14', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=471', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
