(473, 1, '2015-07-08 05:33:51', '2015-07-08 05:33:51', 'Forrest Chase incorporating City Central is located on the corner of Murray St Mall and Perth’s premier civic space, Forrest Place. The centre is home to a select range of fashion and lifestyle offers, including MYER, Ninewest, Witchery, Laura Ashley and Dick Smith’s Electronics. Fitness First Gym can help get you into shape for all that fashion and if you’re looking for food, Han’s Café, Gloria Jeans, Subway, Shimizu Donabe & Bento and Edo Shiki together with Woolworth’s and Woolworth’s liquor, provide a range of food and drinks to suit all.', 'Forrest Chase', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'forrest-chase', '', '', '2015-07-08 05:33:51', '2015-07-08 05:33:51', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=473', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
