(477, 1, '2015-07-08 05:41:14', '2015-07-08 05:41:14', 'The Perth Mint is one of the world’s oldest mints still operating from its original premises, and one of Western Australia’s historic landmarks. The Perth Mint gives visitors the opportunity to experience the excitement of the early gold rushes and be captivated by a traditional gold pouring performance in the original Melting House. Visitors will marvel at the world’s largest collection of gold bars as they gleam from the darkness of the original 1899 vault, and be impressed by the Newmont Normandy Nugget, the second largest nugget in existence weighing a massive 25.5 kilograms. ', 'The Perth Mint', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-perth-mint', '', '', '2015-07-15 06:24:58', '2015-07-15 06:24:58', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=477', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
