(501, 1, '2015-07-08 07:16:04', '2015-07-08 07:16:04', 'The i-City Volunteer Hosts help visitors discover the City of Perth. They staff the City of Perth Information Kiosk in the Murray Street Mall near Forrest Place, and are on hand every day to answer questions about the city. You can take a free orientation walking tour and learn more about the history, arts and culture of Perth on one of four specialty tours of the city. All tours are led by i-City Volunteer Tour guide and they are up to 90 minutes in duration and you meet the tour guide at the kiosk 5 minutes prior to departure. Tours are run 11am Monday to Saturday, or specialty tours 2pm Monday to Friday.', 'iCity Information Kiosk Free Walking Tours', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'icity-information-kiosk-free-walking-tours', '', '', '2015-07-08 07:16:04', '2015-07-08 07:16:04', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=501', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
