(522, 1, '2015-07-08 07:40:10', '2015-07-08 07:40:10', 'Dining in the CBD is now at a whole new level with over fifteen restaurant choices at Brookfield Place. Rooftop bars, cafes and world class restaurants such as Print Hall, The Heriatge and The Trustee. The Precinct is also the destination for a number of new Perth shopping and retail experiences. In between drinks and eats, find new things to do in the city and discover an international standard of fashion, art, cultural exhibitions and ongoing events.', 'Brookfield Place', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brookfield-place', '', '', '2015-07-08 07:40:10', '2015-07-08 07:40:10', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=522', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
