(528, 1, '2015-07-08 08:37:14', '2015-07-08 08:37:14', 'Perth has experienced an explosion of small bars in recent times with funky, gritty, sophisticated, unique and stylish venues popping up all over the city, offering a variety of cuisine choices from casual pizzas and tapas to more sophisticated al la carte, extensive wine lists, cocktails and a good night out. You''ll find a few hidden down the recently refurbished Perth laneways with decorative street art such as Wolf Lane, Howard Lane and Shafto Lane. Download a copy of Show Me Perth''s Small Bar Guide from the above link which features a map and a selection of bars to chose from.', 'Perth Small Bars', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'perth-small-bars', '', '', '2015-07-08 08:38:17', '2015-07-08 08:38:17', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=528', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
