(530, 1, '2015-07-08 08:41:58', '2015-07-08 08:41:58', 'Perth Arena is Western Australia’s landmark home of live entertainment, music and sports, with a 15,500 capacity featuring breathtaking design and world-leading technology. Perth Arena was officially opened in November 2012 and brings major big name concerts and sporting events to Perth all year round. Since the arena opened, artists such as Bruce Springsteen, Beyonce, Pink, Jennifer Lopez, Bon Jovi and Elton John have held concerts here, and in 2014 the Rolling Stones, Justin Timberlake, Robbie Williams and Katy perry are performing at the arena.', 'Perth Arena', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'perth-arena', '', '', '2015-07-08 08:41:58', '2015-07-08 08:41:58', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=530', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
