(542, 1, '2015-07-08 08:56:47', '2015-07-08 08:56:47', 'Through the Collection, the associated programs, and stimulating exhibitions the WA Art Gallery offer visitors unique and exciting experiences of historic and contemporary Australian artists, and bring the art of the world to WA. The WA Art Gallery place particular emphasis on the arts of Australia, but have access to many of the most exciting cultures of the world which adds immeasurably to programs, exhibitions, collections and events at the State Art Gallery. Browse the gallery and enjoy lunch at the cafe or shop for art products and gifts.', 'WA Art Gallery', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wa-art-gallery', '', '', '2015-07-08 08:56:47', '2015-07-08 08:56:47', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=542', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
