(544, 1, '2015-07-09 00:12:30', '2015-07-09 00:12:30', 'Visit the official tourist information centre and talk to the friendly and knowledgeable staff to plan your day out in Fremantle. Located in the heart of Fremantle, next to the Town Hall. The Fremantle Visitor Centre invites you to take in the sights and sound of one of Western Australia’s most historic and beautiful cities. Fremantle is recognised as the best preserved 19th Century seaport in the world, with over 150 buildings in the port city classified by the National Trust. ', 'Fremantle Visitor Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fremantle-visitor-centre', '', '', '2015-07-09 00:12:30', '2015-07-09 00:12:30', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=544', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
