(546, 1, '2015-07-09 00:17:22', '2015-07-09 00:17:22', 'Enjoy breathtaking views of the Indian Ocean, Fishing Boat Harbour, Esplanade Park and the historic city of Fremantle on board one of Fremantle’s most popular tourist attractions, the Tourist Wheel Fremantle. Just a short walk from the Fishing Boat Harbour, the Fremantle Railway Station and the centre of town. Open 6 days a week, subject to change in weather. ', 'Tourist Wheel Fremantle', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tourist-wheel-fremantle', '', '', '2015-07-09 00:17:22', '2015-07-09 00:17:22', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=546', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
