(548, 1, '2015-07-09 00:24:29', '2015-07-09 00:24:29', 'Fremantle Trams run Hop-on-Hop-off guided tours 363 days a year. Taking in all of Fremantle’s famous and historic landmarks, your driver will entertain you with a live commentary along the way. They meet all of the Perth to Fremantle ferries with other conveniently located stops for you to start your tour. On Friday night you can take the Fremantle Tram Ghostly Tour, a torchlight guided tour of Fremantle’s oldest buildings including Fremantle Prison.', 'Fremantle Trams', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fremantle-trams', '', '', '2015-07-09 00:24:29', '2015-07-09 00:24:29', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=548', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
