(554, 1, '2015-07-09 00:30:19', '2015-07-09 00:30:19', 'A warm and friendly welcome awaits you at the Tradewinds Hotel. Overlooking the tranquil waters of the Swan River in East Fremantle, just 30 minutes from Perth. Its accommodation is the perfect place to unwind or celebrate that special occasion. The popular alfresco courtyard is part of the Tradewinds bar & restaurant. It is a delightful setting, day or night. Here you can enjoy a delicious espresso or latte coffee, a casual lunch or dinner chosen from our seasonal menu, or simply relax with friends or business associates after a busy day while watching the sun set over the Indian Ocean beyond Fremantle Harbour.', 'Tradewinds Hotel', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tradewinds-hotel', '', '', '2015-07-09 00:31:58', '2015-07-09 00:31:58', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=554', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
