(556, 1, '2015-07-09 00:34:49', '2015-07-09 00:34:49', 'Business or pleasure, the Hougoumont offers affordable luxury accommodation for the mobile, modern citizen in the heart of Fremantle. Your selection of accommodation comprises Superior Cabin and Stateroom. Opting for style and substance over unnecessary space, each lodging combines luxurious comfort with ultimate connectivity, including smart TVs and free Wi-Fi. Like its nautical namesake, the Hougoumont is manned by a small and dedicated crew, ensuring the highest levels of service and attentiveness.', 'Hougoumont Hotel Fremantle', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hougoumont-hotel-fremantle', '', '', '2015-07-09 00:34:49', '2015-07-09 00:34:49', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=556', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
