(563, 1, '2015-07-09 02:03:46', '2015-07-09 02:03:46', 'Charter 1 offer the choice of two vessels to explore the waters and reefs of award winning Rottnest Island, uninhabited Carnac Island and the stunning Perth Coastline through summer. Join a public Ecotour or Twilight Cruise! We also offer private or corporate functions and luxury liveaboard charters. Through Winter we take you on the adventure of a lifetime to swim with Whale Sharks in Exmouth, or to discover the beautiful Abrolhos Islands off the coast of WA.', 'Charter 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'charter-1', '', '', '2015-07-09 02:03:46', '2015-07-09 02:03:46', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=563', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
