(567, 1, '2015-07-09 02:10:40', '2015-07-09 02:10:40', 'Enjoy a memorable day diving or snorkelling the amazing limestone reefs at Rottnest Island, with world class dive sites so close to Perth City. Dolphin Dive Fremantle operate three fully equipped boats that leave from the Fremantle Port, so a Scuba dive or snorkel out to Rottnest Island is quick and hassle free. Full of schooling fish, rays and sponge gardens, you’ll be amazed while exploring the caves, wrecks and coral. Or simply soak up the sun while the crew cook up a BBQ feast on board the 70ft cat. ', 'Dolphin Dive Fremantle', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dolphin-dive-fremantle', '', '', '2015-07-09 02:10:40', '2015-07-09 02:10:40', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=567', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
