(583, 1, '2015-07-09 02:35:24', '2015-07-09 02:35:24', 'Established in 1985, the friendly staff at Fremantle Opals offer a wealth of knowledge and experience in choosing opals and opal jewellery. They invite you to view an exclusive range of beautiful jewellery and unset opals. Specialists in black opal, Fremantle Opals buy direct from Australian mines, and also offer a range of South sea pearls. You’ll find them at the William Street entrance of the Fremantle Mall, just opposite the Town Hall and a short walk from the railway station. A perfect place to find that special souvenir or gift.', 'Fremantle Opals', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fremantle-opals', '', '', '2015-07-09 02:41:01', '2015-07-09 02:41:01', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=583', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
