(585, 1, '2015-07-09 02:44:17', '2015-07-09 02:44:17', 'Woolstores is home to a extra large Coles Supermarket and over 30 specialty stores as well as casual market stores. The Centre offers customers the convenience of many services ranging from fresh food, liquor, fashion, crafts, homewares, electronics, jewellery, hair stylists, health and beauty and a Ticketek outlet. Located in the heart of Fremantle, open 7 days. Late night trading until 9pm on weekdays, closing 5pm on weekends. ', 'Woolstores Shopping Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'woolstores-shopping-centre', '', '', '2015-07-09 07:13:21', '2015-07-09 07:13:21', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=585', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
