(592, 1, '2015-07-09 04:26:19', '2015-07-09 04:26:19', 'Sourced straight from the ocean and not the freezer, enjoy fresh fish and chips, squid, prawns, seafood burgers and salad cooked and prepared just the way you like it. Processing all of the fish ourselves, we skin, trim and completely de-bone our fresh fish fillets, so there''s nothing to spoil your enjoyment. We guarantee no bones-or your money back and only serve the best Fish & Chips and Seafood! Fishing Boat Harbour Fremantle and Oxford Street in Leederville. Open from 10am 7 days.', 'Sweetlips Fish & Chips', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sweetlips-fish-chips', '', '', '2015-07-09 04:26:19', '2015-07-09 04:26:19', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=592', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
