(594, 1, '2015-07-09 04:29:59', '2015-07-09 04:29:59', 'South Terrace, otherwise known as the ‘Cappuccino Strip’, is a busy cosmopolitan mix of cafes, restaurants and pubs, famous for Fremantle’s Italian influence of pizza and pasta, and the state’s best coffee. With a buzzing atmosphere and choices galore, you’ll also find numerous locally made designer clothes shops, gift and bookstores. South Terrace is also home to the famous Fremantle Markets and the Sail & Anchor Hotel. The perfect spot to find an al-fresco table and watch the eclectic Fremantle world go by.', 'Cappuccino Strip', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cappuccino-strip', '', '', '2015-07-09 04:29:59', '2015-07-09 04:29:59', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=594', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
