(596, 1, '2015-07-09 04:53:16', '2015-07-09 04:53:16', 'Grab a Pale ale and a pizza and soak in the brewery chaos or wander out into the backyard to enjoy your beer and nosh in the sunshine over looking the Fishing Boat Harbour. Make your way over to Creatures Next Door for the harbour views and cosy up with a beer in one of the big lounge chairs. Head to our Brewhouse bar to pick up a six pack to take home or stay awhile for a tasting of our full range of beers. Little Creatures is a very popular tourist attraction and serves tasty and modern cuisine in a bustling and fun atmosphere.', 'Little Creatures', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'little-creatures', '', '', '2015-07-09 04:53:16', '2015-07-09 04:53:16', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=596', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
