(606, 1, '2015-07-09 05:02:03', '2015-07-09 05:02:03', 'Established in 1903, the iconic Cicerello’s is known as WA’s best seafood eatery offering a range of family friendly dining options. With alfresco seating overlooking the scenic Fishing Boat Harbour, Cicerello’s succulent fish and chips are world renowned and not to be missed during your visit to WA. Enjoy freshly caught seafood such as oysters, mussels and crabs with a beer, wine or glass of champagne at the waters edge. ', 'Cicerello''s', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cicerellos', '', '', '2015-07-09 05:02:03', '2015-07-09 05:02:03', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=606', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
