(610, 1, '2015-07-09 06:10:57', '2015-07-09 06:10:57', 'Located over the water at Hillarys Boat Harbour, the multi award winning Breakwater features two levels of dining indulgence both with amazing views across the harbour and out to sea. Whether it’s sipping a beer on the deck as the sun sets, enjoying a cocktail overlooking the harbour, or a special celebration with great food - The Breakwater is the ideal venue. Open 7 days, 11am til late. ', 'The Breakwater', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-breakwater', '', '', '2015-07-22 08:53:21', '2015-07-22 08:53:21', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=610', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(611, 1, '2015-07-09 06:14:07', '2015-07-09 06:14:07', 'Explore 12,000km of Western Australia’s coastline in just one day.From the icy-cold waters of the Southern Ocean to the tropical wonderland of coral reefs in the Far North, AQWA takes you on an underwater journey to discover the fascinating and unique marine life of Western Australia. Highlights of your journey include being surrounded by sharks as you travel beneath Indian Ocean waters in Australia''s largest walk through aquarium, and face a deadly line-up of sea creatures in the DANGERzone. ', 'AQWA', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aqwa', '', '', '2015-07-15 06:30:14', '2015-07-15 06:30:14', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=611', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
