(615, 1, '2015-07-09 06:30:04', '2015-07-09 06:30:04', 'Just 20 minutes north of Perth City lies Scarborough Beach, arguably one of Perth''s most popular beach. With vast sandy beaches and some of Perth''s best breaks, Scarborough is popular with tourists and locals alike. The Scarborough foreshore has undergone a major renovation with many news restaurants, cafes and bars, such as the new Matisse Beach Club. There''s a large range of beachfront accommodation with a host of activities ranging from surfing lessons, bike riding, shopping or attending one of the many free events held in Scarborough during summer.', 'Scarborough Beach', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'scarborough-beach', '', '', '2015-07-09 06:32:17', '2015-07-09 06:32:17', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=615', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
