(620, 1, '2015-07-09 07:12:11', '2015-07-09 07:12:11', 'An enjoyable way to experience the Australian bush, wildflowers and wildlife is by horse back. Ron’s Riding Ranch have access to over 1700 acres of natural bushland and a memorable holiday experience is assured. Experienced staff are on hand to cater for the beginner to the more experienced riders and tours run from an hour and a half to two hours. With beautiful scenery and peaceful encounters with amazing horses, Ron’s Riding Ranch is a special day out with friends and family. ', 'Ron''s Riding Ranch', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rons-riding-ranch', '', '', '2015-07-09 07:12:11', '2015-07-09 07:12:11', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=620', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
