(622, 1, '2015-07-10 00:43:23', '2015-07-10 00:43:23', 'If your holidays are about great fun, great food and great experiences, then you had better not miss a visit to the Wanneroo Botanical Gardens. Come and explore Perth''s most spectacular garden oasis. They guarantee you won''t be disappointed, it''s fun for all ages! Featuring Australia''s largest mini golf course, five acres of stunning botanical gardens and the superb alfresco dining at Leapfrogs Café, it will rate high among your favourite holiday experiences. Located only 25 minutes north of Perth on the Sunset Coast.', 'Wanneroo Botanical Gardens', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wanneroo-botanical-gardens', '', '', '2015-07-10 00:43:23', '2015-07-10 00:43:23', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=622', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
