(626, 1, '2015-07-10 00:52:25', '2015-07-10 00:52:25', 'Looking for a fun, educational day out to entertain the whole family? Whether you are 5 or 50, there is so much to discover at the Gravity Discovery Centre in the beautiful natural bushland west of Gingin, only an hour north of Perth. See science presented in a new and exciting way with hands on exhibits and interactive displays educating people of all ages about our Universe. The centre is located alongside the Gingin Observatory with abundant wildflowers most of the year, peaceful walks in pristine bush, souvenirs to purchase in the gift shop and delicious food and coffees served at Stargazers Cafe. ', 'The Gravity Discovery Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-gravity-discovery-centre', '', '', '2015-07-10 00:52:25', '2015-07-10 00:52:25', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=626', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(627, 1, '2015-07-10 00:52:12', '2015-07-10 00:52:12', '', 'Gingin-Observatory', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'gingin-observatory', '', '', '2015-07-10 00:52:12', '2015-07-10 00:52:12', '', 626, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Gingin-Observatory.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(628, 1, '2015-07-10 00:55:59', '2015-07-10 00:55:59', 'At the Gingin Observatory visitors experience the wonders of space by viewing through telescopes, engaging with astronomers and by interacting during a big screen presentation that highlights our beautiful universe. Their telescopes take you hurtling back in time revealing space as it was thousands years ago. If you''re viewing a star that is 5000 light years away then you are actually seeing the light from that star as it was 5000 thousand years ago because that is how long it takes for that light to reach us here on Earth!', 'Gingin Observatory', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gingin-observatory', '', '', '2015-07-10 00:55:59', '2015-07-10 00:55:59', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=628', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(630, 1, '2015-07-10 00:58:37', '2015-07-10 00:58:37', 'Cervantes Lodge is only 20 minutes (17km) from the famous Pinnacles Desert so perfect for spending some time in the Nambung National Park. Cevantes Lodge features deluxe double rooms with stunning ocean views from prominent locations on Thirsty Point offering a unique outlook over the northern section of the Pinnacles Desert. Staying the night at Cervantes Lodge provides a choice of a self-drive excursion or a day trip to Jurien Bay. ', 'Cervantes Lodge', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cervantes-lodge', '', '', '2015-07-10 00:58:37', '2015-07-10 00:58:37', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=630', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
