(638, 1, '2015-07-10 01:13:10', '2015-07-10 01:13:10', 'Tandem skydive at the World’s Most Beautiful Beach Skydive. Located just 2 hours north of Perth, Skydive Jurien Bay offer beach skydives from up to 14,000ft where you’ll experience the adrenalin rush of freefall over the amazing Coral Coast, a mind-blowing view that has to be seen to be believed. Gift Vouchers and online bookings available.', 'Skydive Jurien Bay', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'skydive-jurien-bay', '', '', '2015-07-10 01:13:10', '2015-07-10 01:13:10', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=638', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
