(644, 1, '2015-07-10 01:58:48', '2015-07-10 01:58:48', 'Morning bus pick up in the city then kayak with our friendly guides at Seal and Penguin Island. See dolphins, sea lions and penguins. Includes lunch, snorkeling gear, penguin feeding and transport. Mention this ad for a 10% discount. Departs Perth daily. ', 'Rivergods Seakayaking', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rivergods-seakayaking', '', '', '2015-07-10 01:58:48', '2015-07-10 01:58:48', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=644', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
