(652, 1, '2015-07-10 02:10:38', '2015-07-10 02:10:38', 'Located on the shores of the Shoalwater Islands Marine Park, Rockingham Wild Encounters operates a ferry service to Penguin Island, home to over 1000 pairs of little penguins. Visitors flock to the island to see the daily penguin feedings at 10.30am, 12.30pm & 2.30pm. A range of other cruises are also available including a glass bottom boat cruise to view Australian Sea Lions, a Dolphin Watch Adventure Cruise and the multi award winning Swim with Wild Dolphins.', 'Rockingham Wild Encounters - Penguin Island', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rockingham-wild-encounters-penguin-island', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:10:38', '2015-07-10 02:10:38', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=652', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(653, 1, '2015-07-10 02:10:28', '2015-07-10 02:10:28', '', 'rockinghamwildencounters', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'rockinghamwildencounters', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:10:28', '2015-07-10 02:10:28', '', 652, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/rockinghamwildencounters.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(654, 1, '2015-07-10 02:17:40', '2015-07-10 02:17:40', 'Rockingham’s calm clear waters are home to over 250 wild bottlenose dolphins. Rockingham Wild Encounters operates a multi award winning dolphin swim cruise that will have these fascinating creatures swimming around within inches of you. First time snorkelers and nervous swimmers are well catered for by experienced guides that use aqua scooters to tow visitors gently amongst the dolphins. This is a must do experience for all wildlife lovers! ', 'Rockingham Wild Encounters - Swim With Dolphins', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rockingham-wild-encounters-swim-with-dolphins', '', '', '2015-07-21 02:20:44', '2015-07-21 02:20:44', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=654', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(655, 1, '2015-07-10 02:17:27', '2015-07-10 02:17:27', '', 'Dolphin-Dive-Fremantle', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'dolphin-dive-fremantle-2', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:17:27', '2015-07-10 02:17:27', '', 654, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Dolphin-Dive-Fremantle1.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(656, 1, '2015-07-10 02:19:32', '2015-07-10 02:19:32', 'The Shoalwater Islands Marine Park is located 50 kilometres south of Perth, adjacent to the City of Rockingham and covers an area of approximately 6658 hectares. The marine park contains a rich diversity and abundance of both marine and terrestrial wildlife, such as seabirds, sea lions (one of the rarest species in the world), dolphins and the Little Penguins who breed on Penguin Island. The cavernous reefs surrounding the islands provide good snorkelling and diving, or you can kayak, swim or relax on the white sandy beaches. Contact Rockingham Wild Encounters for further information.\r\nShoalwater Islands Marine Park', 'Shoalwater Islands Marine Park', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'shoalwater-islands-marine-park', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:19:32', '2015-07-10 02:19:32', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=656', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(657, 1, '2015-07-10 02:19:04', '2015-07-10 02:19:04', '', 'Shoalwater-Marine-Park', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'shoalwater-marine-park', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:19:04', '2015-07-10 02:19:04', '', 656, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Shoalwater-Marine-Park.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(658, 1, '2015-07-10 02:21:58', '2015-07-10 02:21:58', 'The scenic features of Serpentine National Park together with its close proximity to Perth have attracted visitors for almost 100 years. It is also a sanctuary for an array of plants and animals (particularly kangaroos) and has a shaded grassed area popular for picnics. Set in a naturally beautiful cleft at the foot of the scarp, the park stretched up the steep slopes if the Serpentine River valley, past a sheer face of granite polished smooth by the rushing waters. ', 'Serpentine National Park', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'serpentine-national-park', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:21:58', '2015-07-10 02:21:58', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=658', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(659, 1, '2015-07-10 02:21:43', '2015-07-10 02:21:43', '', 'Serpentine-National-Park', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'serpentine-national-park', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:21:43', '2015-07-10 02:21:43', '', 658, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Serpentine-National-Park.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(660, 1, '2015-07-10 02:24:47', '2015-07-10 02:24:47', 'Half hour south of Rockingham, Mandurah is a vibrant tourist destination with plenty of quality waterside restaurants, crystal clear water, numerous activities for the family, plenty of accommodation choices and a relaxed, holiday atmosphere. Enjoy outdoor activities such as fishing, crabbing (in season) swimming, boating or windsurfing. The marina precinct offers waterside leisure, shopping and dining just a short walk from the city centre, or a favourite for visitors is to sip wine on a twilight cruise around the canals and waterways. ', 'Mandurah', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mandurah', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:24:47', '2015-07-10 02:24:47', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=660', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
