(662, 1, '2015-07-10 02:28:49', '2015-07-10 02:28:49', 'Swan Valley’s newest winery, Mandoon Estate offers a unique range of experiences. A la carte fine dining, craft brewery and casual dining, function centre, gourmet deli, Modern Art Galley and kids playground. Open 7 days.', 'Mandoon Estate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mandoon-estate', '', '', '2015-07-22 09:01:06', '2015-07-22 09:01:06', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=662', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(663, 1, '2015-07-10 02:30:34', '2015-07-10 02:30:34', 'A distinctive mix of quality craft, provisions and produce, the Kalamunda Village Markets are held on the first Saturday of each month in the centre of Kalamunda. Visit the market then sample the boutique coffee shops and retail outlets scattered around the town. Run by volunteers from the local Rotary Club, 70% of the funds raised go to local charities. A variety of home-made products, jewellery, gifts are sold along with home-grown fruit and vegetables, providing an enjoyable day out in the Perth Hills. Open from 8.30am to 3.30pm and dates may vary subject to public holidays.', 'Kalamunda Village Market', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kalamunda-village-market', '', '', '2015-07-15 06:46:10', '2015-07-15 06:46:10', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=663', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
