(665, 1, '2015-07-10 02:32:15', '2015-07-10 02:32:15', 'Within an easy 30 minute drive from Perth lies the historic wine region of the Swan Valley, well known world wide for its award winning wines. The region is built on a unique history and heritage blending Indigenous, pioneering colonial and southern European roots and consists of a 32 kilometre loop of more than 200 attractions including wineries, restaurants, cafes, breweries, art galleries, museums, heritage, wildlife and fun for the whole family. Enjoy free tastings such as chocolate, coffee, cheese, honey and nougat. Visit the Swan Valley Visitor Centre, cnr Meadow and Swan Streets, Guildford. ', 'Swan Valley', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'swan-valley', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:32:15', '2015-07-10 02:32:15', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=665', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
