(669, 1, '2015-07-10 02:36:12', '2015-07-10 02:36:12', 'Whiteman Park is a unique tourist attraction located in the Swan Valley and only 25 minutes from Perth. Whiteman Park is set in 4000 hectares of natural bushland, with more than 10 exciting attractions within the park. Bring your picnic, cook up a storm on the BBQ and enjoy the beautiful bushland scenery. Explore the park on foot, bicycle, bus, train or tram. There are 14 kilometres of dual use paths, three bush walking trails, a dog exercise area, Children''s Forest with many other attractions to explore such as the Bird''s of Prey Flying Display, train rides or the Motor Museum of WA. ', 'Whiteman Park', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'whiteman-park', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:36:12', '2015-07-10 02:36:12', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=669', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(670, 1, '2015-07-10 02:35:58', '2015-07-10 02:35:58', '', 'Whiteman-Park-Cycle', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'whiteman-park-cycle', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:35:58', '2015-07-10 02:35:58', '', 669, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Whiteman-Park-Cycle.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(671, 1, '2015-07-10 02:38:42', '2015-07-10 02:38:42', 'Join Chariots of Hire for a brand new Aussie adventure that you will never forget. After teaching you to ride the state-of-the art Chariots, they will lead you through the pristine Aussie bush, taking you over secret wooden bridges and into the naturally cool, shaded wetlands of Whiteman Park, which is home to 150 types of native birds and over 100 species of vertebra. You will glide along many beautiful paths, stopping to see Australian windmills and antique farm machinery, whilst trying to spot the many Kangaroos that will be watching you from amongst the trees! ', 'Chariots of Hire', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'chariots-of-hire', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:38:42', '2015-07-10 02:38:42', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=671', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
