(673, 1, '2015-07-10 02:40:46', '2015-07-10 02:40:46', 'Introducing “SPEED GRAZING” – small groups of 16 explore the awarded Food & Wine Trail of the Swan Valley – Perth’s Valley of Taste - visiting nine delicious locations enjoying more than 25 different tastings in an exciting and fun-filled half day tour twice daily Wednesday to Sunday. Guests sample regional treats like exotic coffees, chocolate coated coffee beans, chocolate, WA cheeses, olives, nougat, ice-cream, honey, lavender scones jam and cream, lavender tea, lavender wine, roasted nuts, bush tucker, premium wines, awarded beers, ginger beer (alcoholic and non) and cider.', 'Taste Bud Tours', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'taste-bud-tours', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:40:46', '2015-07-10 02:40:46', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=673', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
