(675, 1, '2015-07-10 02:42:14', '2015-07-10 02:42:14', 'Within an hour of the CBD, the Perth Hills offer a charming country experience with rolling hills and valleys, stunning scenery, wildflowers and walk trails. Try local platters at a vineyard, a country breakfast at a casual cafe or a ploughmans and a pint at the local pub. There is always something to cater for all tastes and budgets in the Perth Hills. Why not stay a few days in one of the many quality accommodation choices such as a quaint B&B, eco spa retreat or forest chalet, camping grounds or country cottages and homesteads. Kalamunda and Mundaring both have visitor centres with friendly, helpful staff. ', 'Perth Hills', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'perth-hills', '', '', '2015-07-10 02:42:14', '2015-07-10 02:42:14', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=675', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
