(703, 1, '2015-07-10 04:33:25', '2015-07-10 04:33:25', 'Every year Humpback, Southern Right and Blue Whales migrate from the feeding grounds of Antartica to the warmer Indian Ocean waters to breed and give birth off the WA coast. Marvel at these majestic creatures as they playfully breach and frolick; from September to November, they can be viewed just offshore near Perth, and it is a holiday experience definitely not to be missed. See the Rottnest Express and Rottnest fast Ferry listings.', 'Whale Watching', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'whale-watching', '', '', '2015-07-10 04:33:25', '2015-07-10 04:33:25', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=703', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
