(705, 1, '2015-07-10 04:44:18', '2015-07-10 04:44:18', 'Super Roo Tours offer a selection of easy tours to help you experience the best of what Perth has to offer. Visit ten of Perth''s greatest highlights with the Perth Experience Day Tour, including Caversham Wildlife Park and the Swan Valley. Visit the famous Pinnacles and Nambung National Park with the Pinnacles Day Tour and ten of Perth''s best nightspots with the Perth Night Tour which includes fish and chips in Fremantle.', 'Super Roo Tours', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'super-roo-tours', '', '', '2015-07-10 04:44:18', '2015-07-10 04:44:18', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=705', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
