(707, 1, '2015-07-10 04:57:58', '2015-07-10 04:57:58', 'Only ten minutes from the Perth CBD off the Graham Farmer Freeway, Lone Ranger Shooting Gallery offers the chance to uniquely experience real shooting with real guns. Famous guns such as Browning, Beretta, Glock, Ruger, Smith and Wesson, Para Ordnance and the mighty Desert Eagle are at available for hire. There’s also the cowboy lever action rifles, 12 gauge shotguns and .22lr rifles to test your accuracy. ', 'Lone Ranger Shooting Complex', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lone-ranger-shooting-complex', '', '', '2015-07-10 04:57:58', '2015-07-10 04:57:58', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=707', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
