(723, 1, '2015-07-10 07:38:50', '2015-07-10 07:38:50', 'Perth’s place to meet, shop and eat in the city! Fashion, homewares, health & beauty, general retail, bars, restaurants, Coles Central supermarket, a food court and much more! Free wifi and plenty of parking. Raine Square is The Centre of Your City! ', 'Raine Square', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'raine-square', '', '', '2015-07-10 07:38:50', '2015-07-10 07:38:50', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=723', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
