(725, 1, '2015-07-10 08:18:49', '2015-07-10 08:18:49', 'Myer is Australia''s largest department store group and has been synonymous with style and fashion for over 100 years. The Myer merchandise offer includes 11 core product categories: Womenswear, menswear, Miss Shop (youth), childrenswear, intimate apparel, beauty, fragrance and cosmetics, homewares, electrical goods, toys, footwear, handbags and accessories, and general merchandise. You''ll find Myer in Perth City, Morley Galleria, Karrinyup Shopping Centre, Carousel Shopping Centre and Garden City Shopping Centre.', 'Myer Perth', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'myer-perth', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:18:49', '2015-07-10 08:18:49', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=725', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
