(727, 1, '2015-07-10 08:21:09', '2015-07-10 08:21:09', 'The first store opened in Sydney in 1838 by David Jones, a Welsh merchant, with a mission to sell ‘the best and most exclusive goods’. Since then, David Jones has grown to 35 stores, two warehouse outlets and David Jones Online - offering customers the finest brands across fashion, beauty and home. With a rich heritage, they are not only Australia’s oldest department store, but also the oldest department store in the world still trading under its original name. You''ll find David Jones in Perth City, Claremont Quarter, Garden City Shopping Centre and Karrinyup Shopping Centre.', 'David Jones', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'david-jones', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:21:09', '2015-07-10 08:21:09', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=727', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
