(730, 1, '2015-07-10 08:28:05', '2015-07-10 08:28:05', 'Claremont Quarter offers a selection of premium fashion, food, home and lifestyle experiences unlike anything else in Perth. Leading fashion designers and stores such as Morrison, Sass & Bide, Adam Heath, Zara Bryson, Sambag, Zimmerman, Parker & Co, Father and Gorman sit alongside gourmet food options such as Koko Black, Atomic, Beluga, Licquorice and Jack''s Wholefood, and big brands such as David Jones, Country Road, JB Hi Fi, Coles, Rebel and Dick Smith. Claremont Quarter is easily accessible via Stirling Hwy, with a convenient and easy to use carpark and 3 hours free parking. ', 'Claremont Quarter', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'claremont-quarter', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:28:05', '2015-07-10 08:28:05', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=730', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
