(732, 1, '2015-07-10 08:30:54', '2015-07-10 08:30:54', 'Karrinyup Shopping Centre is a regional shopping centre located north of Perth, in the suburb of Karrinyup, approximately 12 kilometres north-west of the Perth CBD, and two kilometres from the ocean to the west. Karrinyup Shopping Centre offers customers a distinctive and inspiring fashion oriented shopping experience and has become a ‘shopper’s paradise’ to many people in Perth. Whether you are a fashionista or looking to equip the family’s clothing needs Karrinyup will be able to satisfy with its many specialty retailers, two department stores and one discount department store.', 'Karrinyup Shopping Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'karrinyup-shopping-centre', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:30:54', '2015-07-10 08:30:54', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=732', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(733, 1, '2015-07-10 08:30:43', '2015-07-10 08:30:43', '', 'Karrinyup-Shopping-Centre', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'karrinyup-shopping-centre', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:30:43', '2015-07-10 08:30:43', '', 732, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Karrinyup-Shopping-Centre.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(734, 1, '2015-07-10 08:38:49', '2015-07-10 08:38:49', 'Westfield Whitford City is a major shopping centre approximately 18 kilometres north west of the Perth CBD on Marmion Avenue in Hillarys. With over 240 specialty stores of fashion, food, electronics, jewellery, accessories, gifts and Grand Cinemas showcasing all the latest movies, you can spend the whole day here! Major retailers at this centre are Myers, Target, Kmart, Coles and Big W. See the website for opening hours.', 'Westfield Whitford City Shopping Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'westfield-whitford-city-shopping-centre', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:38:49', '2015-07-10 08:38:49', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=734', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(736, 1, '2015-07-10 08:45:39', '2015-07-10 08:45:39', 'Westfield Carousel is Perth''s largest shopping centre located just 12 kilometres South East of the Perth CBD and offer Myer, Target, Kmart, Coles, Woolworths, JB Hi-Fi and 220 specialty stores of fashion, beauty, lifestyle and much more. Also within the centre is Hoyts cinema complex with numerous quality restaurants to dine in before a movie. Visit the website for opening hours. ', 'Westfield Carousel Shopping Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'westfield-carousel-shopping-centre', '', '', '2015-07-22 08:59:11', '2015-07-22 08:59:11', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=736', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(738, 1, '2015-07-15 01:31:08', '2015-07-15 01:31:08', 'Garden City would have to be the most stylish of all Perth shopping centres, with high end fashion brands and a classy feel where you know you will find just what you are looking for. Just off the Canning Highway roughly a ten minute drive south of the Perth CBD, Garden City is full of interesting retail stores of fashion, beauty, lifestyle, computers, food, surf stores, jewellery, gifts and much more. Garden City is open 7 days and offers plenty of parking. There''s also a cinema complex, David Jones, Myers and Apple Computers. Visit the website for opening hours.', 'Garden City Shopping Centre', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'garden-city-shopping-centre', '', '', '2015-07-22 08:58:33', '2015-07-22 08:58:33', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=738', 0, 'directories', '', 0);
