(740, 1, '2015-07-15 01:34:47', '2015-07-15 01:34:47', 'Perth and Fremantle offer a fine selection of markets, which offer a pleasurable alternative to city shopping. Get a taste of regional fresh produce, arts and crafts, antiques, paintings, music, books, jewellery and hand made Australian products. The famous Fremantle Markets, established in 1897, is a must see destination with over 150 stalls, including fresh vegetables, local cheese, honey, bread and the smell of fresh coffee in the air. Other markets with much to offer are the E Shed Markets at Victoria Quay in Fremantle, and the Station Street Markets in Subiaco. Most markets are open from Friday to Sunday.', 'Markets', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'markets', '', '', '2015-07-15 01:34:47', '2015-07-15 01:34:47', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=740', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
