(742, 1, '2015-07-15 01:36:43', '2015-07-15 01:36:43', 'Art is central to Aboriginal culture. It was used to record and pass the beliefs and stories from one generation to another. If you are looking to purchase an authentic Australian souvenir or gift while visiting WA, you can’t get more true to the heart of Australia than an aboriginal painting or sculpture. There are many galleries to chose from: the Aboriginal Art and Craft Gallery in Kings Park is a good start, or try Creative Native in Forrest Chase, Didgeridoo Breath or Artitja Fine Art in Fremantle, or pop into the Visitor Centre on William Street, Perth for more options.', 'Aboriginal Art', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aboriginal-art', '', '', '2015-07-15 01:36:43', '2015-07-15 01:36:43', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=742', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
