(744, 1, '2015-07-15 01:38:01', '2015-07-15 01:38:01', 'Australia produces 95% of the world’s precious opal, which is why they make such a special gift or souvenir of your visit to Australia. With the increasing scarcity of gem quality opals, it may soon become the most sought after and precious of all gems. It takes salt, water, sand and approximately 50 million years to form an opal! They are 60% as strong as diamond and twice as strong as your teeth. Visit Helen and Daryl at Fremantle Opals, William Street in Fremantle who are experts in opal creation with a large display of beautifully crafted opal jewellery, all uniquely Australian.', 'Opals', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'opals', '', '', '2015-07-15 01:38:01', '2015-07-15 01:38:01', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=744', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(745, 1, '2015-07-15 01:37:46', '2015-07-15 01:37:46', '', 'Opals', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'opals', '', '', '2015-07-15 01:37:46', '2015-07-15 01:37:46', '', 744, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Opals.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(746, 1, '2015-07-15 01:42:36', '2015-07-15 01:42:36', 'The award winning Matisse Beach Club is an exclusive mecca of glamour, light and fluid cool. Offering chic cabanas and lounges nestled by sparkling aqua pools, you can sip a cocktail and enjoy delicious casual dining. You can also make a reservation in our dedicated dining area. Open 7 days. ', 'Matisse Beach Club', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'matisse-beach-club', '', '', '2015-07-22 08:51:08', '2015-07-22 08:51:08', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=746', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(747, 1, '2015-07-15 01:47:11', '2015-07-15 01:47:11', 'The Trustee’s much loved little brother The Beaufort Street Merchant, is a Mount Lawley institution. Rustic, peasant dishes for breakfast lunch and dinner and seriously good coffee. Brasserie, bar, wine shop and provedore, this space is buzzing with locals from morning to night, serving up dishes such as coq au vin pie and cassoulet. Shelves are stacked with handmade pasta, premium olive oils, cookbooks and an expert selection of wines. Busy early til late 7 days from 7am. ', 'The Beaufort Street Merchant', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-beaufort-street-merchant', '', '', '2015-07-22 08:43:38', '2015-07-22 08:43:38', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=747', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(748, 1, '2015-07-15 02:20:22', '2015-07-15 02:20:22', 'At The Old Brewery we serve real food, taken to heights which delight even the most sophisticated palate – without the ‘gastro babble’. The reason we’ve been named WA’s “Best Steak Restaurant” in Perth four times in a row is quite simple; we serve only the best steak, cooked to perfection and presented by some of the best people in the business. And we work hard to make it seem so simple. We want your experience at The Old Brewery to be the best of dining memories, fabulous food with great service in one of the most spectacular riverside locations to be found around the glorious city of Perth. ', 'The Old Brewery Grill', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-old-brewery-grill', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:20:22', '2015-07-15 02:20:22', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=748', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
(749, 1, '2015-07-15 02:20:02', '2015-07-15 02:20:02', '', 'The-Old-Brewery', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-old-brewery', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:20:02', '2015-07-15 02:20:02', '', 748, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/The-Old-Brewery.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(750, 1, '2015-07-15 02:23:14', '2015-07-15 02:23:14', 'Welcome to Fraser’s – a place that celebrates the best Western Australia has to offer in food, wine and service, set in one of the most spectacular locations in the state, at Kings Park over looking the city. Fraser’s is the perfect place to celebrate, dine and create lasting memories. The beautiful environs of Fraser’s are matched perfectly with exceptional food and wine. Executive chef Chris Taylor uses the best West Australian produce in his award-winning cuisine, with a philosophy that allows the produce to speak for itself – honest flavours, simply yet deftly prepared and respectfully handled.\r\nFraser''s Restaurant', 'Fraser''s Restaurant', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'frasers-restaurant', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:23:14', '2015-07-15 02:23:14', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=750', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
