(753, 1, '2015-07-15 02:33:59', '2015-07-15 02:33:59', 'CBD Restaurant & Bar is located on the corner of King and Hay Streets, just a short stroll from Perth''s shopping malls, Swan River and the Kings Park Botanic Gardens. Nestled amongst the 20th Century architecture in one of the most exclusive addresses in Perth, the award winning CBD Restaurant & Bar is the ideal location for chic entertainment and dining, with a relaxed alfresco feel, combining the best of modern city living and boutique café culture. Whether you''re after a great coffee, sensational meal or a relaxing drink at the end of the day, CBD Restaurant & Bar in the centre of Perth has it all!', 'CBD Restaurant & Bar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cbd-restaurant-bar', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:33:59', '2015-07-15 02:33:59', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=753', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
