(755, 1, '2015-07-15 02:40:19', '2015-07-15 02:40:19', 'With fantastic views across the beautiful Swan river to South Perth, The Lucky Shag Waterfront Bar is truly a unique venue in the city. From its relaxed atmosphere during the day to the vibrant feel of the evening there is no better place for lunch, dinner, functions or just to wind down with a few drinks. There''s live entertainment up to 4 nights a week, from bands to D.J''s , and big screens and plasmas to watch all the sports action. Our Pub Grub menu caters to the hungry and for a lot less than you''d expect to pay at such a great located venue. ', 'Lucky Shag Waterfront Bar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lucky-shag-waterfront-bar', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:40:19', '2015-07-15 02:40:19', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=755', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
