(757, 1, '2015-07-15 02:42:41', '2015-07-15 02:42:41', 'Originally built in 1889, The Queens is a contemporary pub with timeless style, where food, friendly staff and great beer come together as one. The Queens lives up to its reputation as one of Perth’s premier venue. Snacking, dining or savoring... what ever your mood, the Queens is the perfect place to relax, enjoy and satisfy. A la carte and bar snack menus are offered throughout the venue from 11am Monday to Friday and 8.30am for breakfast on Sunday and Monday public holidays. Dine inside or in the beer garden overlooking buzzing Beaufort Street.', 'The Queens', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-queens', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:42:41', '2015-07-15 02:42:41', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=757', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
