(763, 1, '2015-07-15 02:49:22', '2015-07-15 02:49:22', 'In the heart of Highgate’s buzzing Beaufort Street, just a stone’s throw from the Perth CBD, is a little slice of Paris. Must is as its name suggests – more than Perth’s number one winebar, it’s also one of the city’s most fashionable bistros and home to the best French provincial-inspired food this side of Provence. Must Wine Bar’s dining space is casual and friendly, and offers a sophisticated dining experience, matching a carefully curated wine list with sublime French bistro food. Open 7 days, noon to midnight. ', 'Must Wine Bar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'must-wine-bar', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:49:22', '2015-07-15 02:49:22', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=763', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
