(765, 1, '2015-07-15 02:51:15', '2015-07-15 02:51:15', 'Mille Café is renowned among the locals and visitors alike for its consistency in service and cuisine, and has the awards to reflect its achievements. This is the perfect restaurant for an intimate dinner with that special person or just relax over lunch or dinner with a group of friends. All this is complimented by the friendly staff and great service. Mille Café is located opposite the Civic Hotel on Beaufort Street with ample parking near by. We allow BYO wine only at $5/bottle and have an affordable wine list. ', 'Mille Cafe', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mille-cafe', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:51:15', '2015-07-15 02:51:15', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=765', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
