(768, 1, '2015-07-15 02:52:47', '2015-07-15 02:52:47', 'Indiana is an iconic West Australian landmark located on the pristine white sands of Cottesloe Beach. Offering diners uninterrupted views of the Indian Ocean from all tables, Indiana provides a picturesque setting to enjoy any special occasion. Our menu focuses on fresh WA produce with our food philosophy being “less is more”, by treating the ingredients with integrity and letting the produce speak for itself. Indiana offers a fantastic shared style menu, including wood fired delicacies; charcuterie style items and local seafood. We aim to keep the overall feel relaxed; perfect for our beachfront location.', 'Indiana Cottesloe Beach', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'indiana-cottesloe-beach', '', '', '2015-07-15 02:52:47', '2015-07-15 02:52:47', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Helloperth/php/?post_type=directories&#038;p=768', 0, 'directories', '', 0),
